{"tid":1421551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機場集會越快搞越好","createTime":"2019-08-06T08:21:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T11:36:54.000Z","uid":32469,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c751a6acc8f0da038bfbcd0a9b6e929861f6b220","tid":1421551,"uid":32469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:21:54.000Z","msg":"呢個po係呼應以下我呢個po<br />\n<br />\n統戰和理非及勇武之拙見<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1417737\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1417737</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n首先我地要肯定尋日85三罷同遍地開花抗爭行動嘅效果，雖然唔係完美，但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">絕非唔成功</span></span>，要多謝一眾勇士及和理非團結行動。檢討野我唔係呢到講，我想講嘅係<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">後續行動</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">如果大家冇睇我上面個po，請大家睇左先。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n小弟認為<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">盡快排程舉行大型機場集會係上策</span></span></strong>，原因有三<br />\n<br />\n一:<br />\n機場集會能<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">吸納大量和理非參與</span></span></strong>，和理非參與度嘅重要性請睇返我上面個po<br />\n<br />\n二:<br />\n航空業/空中服務業係最早及聲勢最大響應罷工行動。和平機場集會係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">回報返業界對運動支持</span></span></strong>嘅一個好方法，同時展示團結各界別人士嘅意念。當日應該開咪讚揚各界人士響應，正式感謝市民，肯定團結力量，並特別提及航空業嘅支持。種種行動都好適合和理非去做，提高返和理非係運動嘅角色。<br />\n<br />\n三:<br />\n之前有多個po都有講，機場對政府打擊大，但對廣大市民生活冇直接影響。換句話說，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">成本低，效益高</span></span></strong>。而且大家都見政府冷處理機場集會，佢乜都遣責，但好似冇遣責過我地所謂搞亂機場。明顯地佢地策略上避談機場，咁我地就要逼佢出聲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>留意返，我冇叫勇武唔好做野</strong></span></span>，勇武做唔做野佢地自己會有分數，香港人政治智慧已經浮現，唔洗多講。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總結: <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非全面進場，勇武整裝待發</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"0391e1159c44f3e334069ff96376c92b2d5fbbc4","tid":1421551,"uid":32469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:23:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"319369f113cd671ee84d4a90f18091a12990a8c1","tid":1421551,"uid":39568,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:23:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong>推晒所有機場post<br />\n8月9-11日<br />\n和理非進場<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WFeQsAz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWFeQsAz.jpg&h=ead62688&s={SIZE}\" /></strong></strong></span>"},{"pid":"25f6c52d5eea1078dcc364e88b4c9fd5b29fdf7b","tid":1421551,"uid":32469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:25:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54dd3cb276db87f313aa209d685bb0582f4b5b13","tid":1421551,"uid":32469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:28:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ad88eed06aacfef6c5cba8803e6b5df04a07fd9","tid":1421551,"uid":32469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:29:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e5abfbba0bf77a7413b9f1ee45dbb10474b4194","tid":1421551,"uid":32469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:32:23.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0deb633116d1e2431c88bb8a303e6db777b3d386","tid":1421551,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:39:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8971036a7c15fd79b2c551c1efea329a7bc64e39","tid":1421551,"uid":32469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:46:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"722942e3519dabcce52b758f63bf7d0f131562f2","tid":1421551,"uid":810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:46:30.000Z","msg":"9號入機場，準備多國語言文宣，幫我手一齊推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"540356c42c2033f893ba545d